He's a Xantista. Let's kill him now!

171
00:23:32,960 --> 00:23:35,960
Yes, let's kill him! Shut up!

172
00:23:39,670 --> 00:23:43,660
You are accused of killing two
of our men, down at the station.

173
00:23:44,610 --> 00:23:46,340
