squashing of the head...

206
00:26:22,680 --> 00:26:25,300
...of this son of a penguin!

207
00:26:28,250 --> 00:26:33,740
- For General Mongo, charge!
- Let's go!

208
00:26:45,500 --> 00:26:48,900
Get rid of that old jalopy!
Get it out!

209
00:26:49,300 --> 00:26:51,200
